  "text": "X NH4 is an efficiency factor of NH + 4 in comparison to NO − 3 , which was assumed that X NH4 is equal to 6 [CITATION_1] . Actually, there is a controversy over the negligible canopy uptake of NO − 3 . Up to now, several basic assumptions in the model (e.g. the ratio in exchange efficiency between H + and NH + 4 ) are not properly evaluated for different environmental conditions (tree species, ecological setting and pollution climate) which limit its application [CITATION_2] .",
